
1. To create the script with .sh and give the execution permission.(ugo+x)
2.  command ->  zip path/zipped-file.zip list-of-file-to-zip
3. command ->   scp hostname@ip-address:file-to-send
4. for passwordless, create ssh-keygen and use ssh-copy-id  user@ip-address to place in authorized user folder. 
